{"word":"G5535 - χρῄζω - chrḗizō - khrade'-zo - Need","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χρῄζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chrḗizō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khrade'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Need</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வேண்டியதாயிரு, தேவையான தாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to have need of, to be in want of"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5532 - χρεία - chreía - khri'-ah/5532\">G5532</a>; to <i>make</i> (that is, <i>have</i>) <i>necessity</i>, that is, <i>be in want</i> of: - (have) need.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}